        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer30326824" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15768268382985560784">3.0 to 3.5 stars. Not quite as enjoyable as Fforde&apos;s other novels (my favorite being <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6628.The_Big_Over_Easy__Nursery_Crime___1_' title='The Big Over Easy (Nursery Crime, #1) by Jasper Fforde' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Big Over Easy</a>) but still a good read. I really like the &quot;world&quot; of Thursday next and will certainly visit it again by reading the next book in the series. </span>
  <span id="freeText15768268382985560784" style="display:none">3.0 to 3.5 stars. Not quite as enjoyable as Fforde's other novels (my favorite being <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6628.The_Big_Over_Easy__Nursery_Crime___1_" title="The Big Over Easy (Nursery Crime, #1) by Jasper Fforde" rel="nofollow noopener">The Big Over Easy</a>) but still a good read. I really like the "world" of Thursday next and will certainly visit it again by reading the next book in the series. </span>
